    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>We have quite the same hot sauce in north Africa, it&#8217;s called Harissa but instead of using water we use olive oil and we don&#8217;t use pumpkin seeds. The texture of it is thick and more red than orange. Even though i am not a spice amateur I like this one because it&#8217;s more aromatic than hot.</p>
    </div>

